Even positions (2nd & 4th): 4 + 2 = 6

Now, is 4422 the largest permutation of [4,2,2,4] divisible by 11? All permutations of [4,2,2,4] sorted descending: 4422, 4242, 4224, 2442, 2424, 2244.
